```python
# Binary Search 7
def binary_search7(arr, x):
    l, r = 0, len(arr)-1
    while l <= r:
        mid = (l + r) // 2
        if arr[mid] == x:
            return True
        elif arr[mid] < x:
            l = mid + 1
        else:
            r = mid - 1
    return False
print('Binary search:', binary_search7(list(range(10)), 7))
```
